			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p28786" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>8</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://novejshaaj.mybb.ru/viewtopic.php?id=1027#p28786">2013-11-30 09:55:47</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
